title: 12-year old Belgium supergrom Dean Vandewalle in Hawaii
description:
Our 12-year old microgram Dean Vandewalle hails from Belgium and has been shaped by living and surfing in Costa Rica. He spent some time on the North Shore of Hawaii this winter and this is his classy edit from the trip. The quote of the video has to be: "I forgot to pack my brown coloured shorts because I might be needing them!'
Check it out and don't feel too bad about a 12 year old that surfs so good.
